lead_paragraph: Paraguayan state prosecutors on Thursday raided the headquarters of South American football confederation CONMEBOL after a request for cooperation from U.S. justice officials probing corruption inside world football, the prosecution office said.

headline.print_headline: Paraguay Officials Raid South American Football Confederation CONMEBOL
